public interface NameTag
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject

A representation of the model object 'Name Tag'. This is the base class for all elements in a network container. Id is for identification purpose. For each type of element, id has to be unique. name and desc are optional. Status is for turning a element on/off.

The following features are supported:

  • Id
  • Name
  • Desc
  • Number
  • Status

See Also:
NetPackage.getNameTag()
